Energy

Summary of who wasted the most energy and who cost the enemy the most energy.
Calculated by adding up Losses (and Stalemates, Defends, Escapes, Interrupts) and Defends, the multiplying the number by 25.
E_Wasted means the member spent X energy on attacks that failed.
E_Stolen means X energy was wasted by the enemy on attacking the member unsuccessfully.
You might want to take a closer look at members with high E_Wasted values and remind them to pick fights they can win!

1 These numbers will be 0 if you are using an API key WITHOUT faction access.

AI summary (BETA)

This is an experimental portion of the report - an overview of the war generated by AI.
When looking at this section, keep that in mind and take the results with a grain of salt.
Before taking any actions that might impact faction members mentioned in this summary, double-check that there are no mistakes or missed key details.

Here is a summary of the provided combat data:

Overall Faction Performance

The faction shows a moderate level of engagement with a good proportion of members participating in war hits. A positive aspect is the relatively low number of energy wasted, suggesting efficient target selection. The faction's overall Net_Score is positive, indicating that their attacks are generally more successful than unsuccessful.

Areas for Improvement

There is room for improvement in team play, as assists are generally low across the board. Some members are incurring a high number of hospital visits, which affects overall performance. Additionally, some members have a high number of losses, indicating that they are attacking targets that are too difficult. The faction could benefit from better coordination and target selection strategies to minimize losses and maximize efficiency.

Individual Highlights: Positive

  • cutt: High War_Hits (47), decent Assists (2), good Activity (4.656 hours), and a very high Net_Score (421.38) with a high FairFight (2.69). This member was highly effective.
  • Supreme_: High War_Hits (65), decent Assists (2), very high Activity (15.446 hours), and a high Net_Score (373.24) with good FairFight (1.85). A highly active and effective player.
  • Merle-DicksIn: Good War_Hits (41), some Assists (3), and a high Net_Score (238.57). Showed good performance during the war.
  • Harleequiin: Decent War_Hits (17), good Non_War_Hits (19), and a positive Net_Score (84.93). Showed a good balance of war and non-war activity.
  • EYJL: 15 War Hits with a good Net_Score (97.33).

Individual Highlights: Negative

  • ThePickles: Very high Hospital visits (40) and a negative Net_Score (-45.07). Needs to improve survivability or target selection.

  • FogBorne: High E_Wasted (30.18), and a negative Net_Score (-30.18).

Additional Observations

  • Several members have a high number of hospital visits relative to their Net_Score, indicating that they may be taking unnecessary risks or selecting inappropriate targets.
  • A few members used boosters and cans during the war, but overall usage was low, suggesting that the faction may not be fully utilizing these resources to maximize their effectiveness.
  • The_Totem, Goose_wayne, FogBorne, MrLuther, SixtenBlixt, Mystic_Music did not have any war hits.
